## Examples

- `type:decision status:open` ŌĆö All open decisions
- `creator:@alice sort:newest` ŌĆö Alice's content, newest first
- `"project update" type:note after:-7d` ŌĆö Notes containing "project update" from the last 7 days
- `collective:my-team group:type` ŌĆö All content in my-team, grouped by type
- `visibility:private` ŌĆö Only content in your private workspace
- `-visibility:private` ŌĆö Everything except your private workspace
